21 passed and approved, then [section 1 of this act] must be amended as follows:
22 "Section 1. Transfer of funds. Within 15 days of [the effective date of this act], the state treasurer
23 shall transfer $50 $10 million from the general fund to the housing Montana fund provided for in 90-6-133."
24
